248
00:16:24,255 --> 00:16:25,207
Yes.

249
00:16:25,874 --> 00:16:27,428
Why wouldn't you be able to, son?

250
00:16:27,588 --> 00:16:28,715
That time,

251
00:16:28,894 --> 00:16:30,634
I saw you practicing the drums.

252
00:16:30,658 --> 00:16:32,358
Like, boom, bap, boom boom.

253
00:16:32,505 --> 00:16:34,213
You were amazing.

254
00:16:35,317 --> 00:16:37,105
- Isn't that right, dear?
- That's right.

255
00:16:37,438 --> 00:16:39,010
Our son is so talented.

256
00:16:39,876 --> 00:16:42,972
But if I have a band,

257
00:16:42,996 --> 00:16:44,437
and I practice with my friends,

258
00:16:44,461 --> 00:16:45,761
